docker pull <image name> => to pull image from dockerhub
docker run <image name>  => to run a container
docker run -d <image name>  => to run a container in a detached mode
docker run -d -p <hostport:containerport> <image name>  => to run a container in a detached mode and port forward
docker run -d -p <hostport:containerport> --name <containername> <image name>  => to run a container in a detached mode and port forward and name
docker stop <container name | container id> stop a container 
docker exec -it <container id> /bin/sh => to open interactive shell inside the container
docker ps => to list all running containers
